text:
Kardashian Family Vacation in Costa Rica January 2017 The Kardashian-Jenner Clan Jets Off to Costa Rica For Some Family Fun January 28, 2017 Share This Link Copy What’s Your Reaction? Thanks for your reaction Don’t forget to share this with your friends! ← Use Arrows Keys → 1 The Kardashian-Jenner Clan Jets Off to Costa Rica For Some Family Fun 
The Kardashian-Jenner clan fled the country's cold Winter temperatures when they touched down in Costa Rica this week. Not only did Kylie and Kourtney put their enviable bikini bodies on display on Instagram, but Kim shared Snapchat videos of her kids, North and Saint West, and her workout session with Khloé. It's been reported that Kanye West did not join them as he's busy working on new music in LA, but Scott Disick, Tyga, and Corey Gamble did tag along. Their trip is being shot for Keeping Up With the Kardashians , which recently resumed filming after taking a break following Kim's Paris robbery . Related:
